    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>I am writing to say how much I am enjoying Melissa Clark's ''Good Appetite'' column. The writing is crisp and personal, and the recipes are wonderful. She really captures the essence of why and how so many of us enjoy playing with our food.</p>
        <p>Karen Brack  Garland, Tex.</p>
      </block>
